title: Star Trek TNG - 03x06 Booby Trap - HQ x264 ac3 5.1 Smooth Motion
description:
NEW Star Trek The Next Generation 24p Smooth Motion Rips - No Blending! 

FINALLY a High Quality, Motion Corrected 24p x264 1000kbps encode, with both original ac3 audio tracks (5.1 and 2.0)
